    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sound E46 M3, featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six power plant. This unit remains naturally aspirated, utilizing its factory individual throttle bodies for exceptional throttle response. Critical preventative maintenance has been prioritized: the VANOS system has been overhauled with upgraded seals and the rear subframe has been professionally reinforced to ensure structural integrity under lateral load. The drivetrain features the desirable ZF 6-speed manual transmission feeding power through a GKN limited-slip differential. The suspension geometry is maintained via a recent refresh of the bushings and the installation of Bilstein dampers, providing a taut, communicative ride. While the finish shows minor road-derived patina, the mechanical components are dialed in for peak performance and longevity.",
