      "description": "This vehicle represents a fantastic opportunity for a discerning buyer looking for a reliable and aesthetically pleasing ride. The exterior retains its original deep luster, though a close inspection reveals a few minor stone chips on the front bumper consistent with light highway use. Inside, the cabin is a sanctuary of comfort; the premium leather seats are in excellent shape, with only slight softening of the leather on the driver\u2019s side bolster. All onboard technology, from the infotainment system to the dual-zone climate control, operates flawlessly. Mechanically, the car is sound, having undergone regular synthetic oil changes and all scheduled maintenance intervals. The tires have plenty of tread remaining on the alloy wheels, and the brake pads were recently serviced for crisp stopping power. Included with the sale is a complete folder of service records, ensuring peace of mind for the next owner. This is a solid, honest car that drives as well as it looks.",
